<p>United HealthCare is a company that knows how to &quot;chart a
course of constant renewal and to work to sustain cultures that
produce the very best products and people.&quot; - <i>Fortune</i>
</p>

<p>At United HealthCare there is no resource more valuable than
our people. It is the talent and thoughtware -- the collective
knowledge, training and experience of our people -- that will
enable us to move ahead. With the resources of a powerful
international organization, we foster a supportive, flexible
culture that encourages participation, development and career
advancement. </p>

<ul>
    <li><a href="#current">Current Opportunities</a></l</ul>

